          "description": "This is the worst place I\u2019ve ever been to in my life. I called Friday about an emergency contraceptive and begged them to please send a new one that day because it was an emergency. They didn\u2019t fill it until that Monday and all the nurse \u201cwe sorry how do you feel about that\u201d I hung up on that lady face. Then some man called me on the same bs. Like what I\u2019m supposed to do?? I can\u2019t take it now so it ain\u2019t no point of calling my pharmacist I can\u2019t take it.",
