          "description": "I\u2019ve been going here for over 10 years off and on. First, they don\u2019t have enough appointments for the medical recommendations and treatments they prescribe because they\u2019re always canceling appointments at the last min at least for dental. This leaves one with anxiety and constantly out of care. But the dental work is good if you can get it constantly. Good luck. Less chatting gets you more. Primary care is shift as well and most of the time they are rude practitioners because they\u2019re pushing patient after patient. Still better than nothing\u2026",
