          "description": "Though I don't go there often, I can say that I've taken my daughter there through the years and now she takes her children.  The front staff can be iffy when they are overwhelmed.  You can see the push for them to be nice and that still needs some work.  The main complaint I have is that they only have 1 dentist who is actually very good and she is pleasant.  The problem being the ONLY dentist is that their appointments are 3 - 4 months from the time you call.   I just called and the woman told me the end of June or sometime in July.  Not good!!!!!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURBd2FlTFV3EAE!2m1!1s0x0:0xadae923df112112c!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgIDAwaeLUw%7C%7C?hl=en",
