          "description": "The service was horrible, customer service was rude and they rescheduled my dentist appointment 3 times, and I had to wait months for the next appointment. I don't have issuance so in that time rates increased and I asked for a discount due to them rescheduling me and they declined.  Once I finally made it to my appointment the new dentist was rude and overworked. She even had the audacity to ask if I wouldn't mind rescheduling my appointment. I refused, she cleaned my teeth but her equipment din't even work. The hygienist was training, which annoyed me because they conversed in Spanish the entire time which I thought was rude. They were clearly using me to help this young lady learn the ropes, which would have been fine if I was at dental school and paying half price. They take advantage of the fact that they are across from the projects. Thankfully I will be getting new issuance soon and will never return. This place is disgusting and needs to be reviewed by the dept of health.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUN3Nk1XcThRRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xadae923df112112c!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgICw6MWq8QE%7C%7C?hl=en",
